{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1ffbb9ede3","title":"湖南召开贫下中农代表会议","origin":"美国图书馆收藏","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"167943e1c4","index":0,"year":1964,"month":3,"day":13,"articleId":"1ffbb9ede3"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"cd89ac037e","name":"肖彦"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"06496790b9","type":"title","text":"湖南召开贫下中农代表会议","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"1ffbb9ede3"},{"id":"36f118a3e3","type":"authors","text":"肖彦","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"1ffbb9ede3"},{"id":"d643ee8f53","type":"paragraph","text":"湖南省委召开的贫下中农代表会议，三月五日在长沙开幕。会议主要讨论在当前国内外大好形势下，依靠贫下中农大搞阶级斗争、生产斗争和科学实验三大革命运动的问题，以及讨论在全省深入开展学习解放军、开展比学赶帮和“五好”竞赛活动的问题。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"1ffbb9ede3"},{"id":"16697a026b","type":"paragraph","text":"这次开会的目的：一是撑腰，党撑贫下中农的腰，就要坚持贯彻党的依靠贫下中农，团结中农的阶级路线；贫下中农撑党的腰，就是拥护党，依靠党的领导。二是取经，就是交流经验，互相学习，大家都当学生，大家都当先生，比学赶帮，好上加好。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"1ffbb9ede3"},{"id":"32f7bc9ae8","type":"paragraph","text":"出席这次会议的，有汉、苗、土家、侗、瑶、回六个民族的代表一千三百八十五人。（新华社湖南分社肖彦）","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"1ffbb9ede3"},{"id":"24687a512a","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：１９６４年３月１３日新华社《内部参考》。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"1ffbb9ede3"}],"page":{"id":"913707fc07","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"1ffbb9ede3","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}